<!--
  Editor <-> headless-core D-Bus interface (#457). The wire form of the contract
  in src/shared/core-contract.ts.

  Methods are a UNIFORM JSON RPC so the server dispatcher is generic (one code
  path over CORE_METHODS): every method takes one "args" string (the logical
  arguments JSON-encoded as an array; empty array for no-arg methods) and returns
  one "result" string (the result JSON-encoded; "null" for void methods). See
  core-contract.ts for the decoded argument + result types.

  Signals are push (core -> editor); their payload is a JSON string, except
  ActionsChanged which carries none. Service org.spaceux.Core, object
  /org/spaceux/Core.
-->
<node>
